   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,410:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Goal:
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,412:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Replace the Mamba+LLM gated fusion architecture with a dual-arm system (Mamba behavioral +
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,412:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: BGE/FAISS content tower), combined at a reranker layer.
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,413:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Architecture:
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,420:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Two independent arms — Mamba4Rec predicts from interaction sequences, Content Tower retrieves by
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,428:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: semantic similarity. A reranker blends scores with implicit alpha based on query specificity. Graduation mechanism
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,429:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: promotes new movies into Mamba
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,429:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
