   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,752:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     def encode_query(self, query: str) -> torch.Tensor:
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,753:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         """Encode a user search query.
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,753:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         BGE recommends prefixing queries with an instruction
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:08,754:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         for asymmetric retrieval tasks.
