   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,078:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     ) -> List[Dict]:
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,078:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         """Search the content index.
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,079:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         Args:
