   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,081:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: normalized).
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,081:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:             alpha: Blend weight — 1.0 = query only, 0.0 = profile
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,082:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: only.
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,082:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:             top_k: Number of results to return.
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,083:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         Returns:
