   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,110:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     def get_movie_embedding(self, movie_id: int) ->
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,111:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Optional[np.ndarray]:
