   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,299:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         top_k: int = 10,
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,300:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     ) -> List[Dict]:
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,300:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         """Rank movies for a group using fairness-weighted
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,301:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: aggregation.
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,301:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         Args:
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,302:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:             per_user_scores: {movie_id: [user1_score, user2_score,
