   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,614:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: alpha=alpha, top_k=top_k)
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,615:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         return results
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,615:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:     def recommend_group(
   DEBUG: 2026-02-20 18:00:09,615:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:         self,
